channel.name: Channel Manager
channel.description:
The channel manager application really has been superseded by Iguana 6's built in ability to import and export channels.
But if you used Iguana 5 and the channel manager to save channels then you need something to load that format back into Iguana. So that is the reason for having this.
This is really just intended to allow you to migrate existing channels, so I think it works.

from_http.commit_comment: Import Translators: Imported John Scalise's channels.
